### 1. Backup Current Store
```bash
cp src/lib/cart-store.ts src/lib/cart-store.ts.backup
```

### 2. Copy New Implementation
```bash
# Copy content from improved-cart-store.ts
```

### 3. Update Usage in Components
```typescript
// Before
const items = useCart((s) => s.items);
const count = useCart((s) => s.count());

// After (still works, but can be optimized)
const items = useCart(cartSelectors.selectItems);
const count = useCart(cartSelectors.selectItemCount);
```

